  "description": "Muyuan Foods Co., Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, operates as a pork company in the hog farming industry in China. It operates through four segments: hog business, slaughtering and meat product business, feed ingredients trading, and others. The company engages in breeding and sales of piglets, finished hogs, breeding hogs, meat products and by-products, hog carcasses, pork cuts, and raw material for feed, pig manure, and feed products, as well as slaughtering and meat production, and fresh and frozen meat products. The company was formerly known as Henan Muyuan Foods Co., Ltd and changed its name to Muyuan Foods Co., Ltd. in February 2002. Muyuan Foods Co., Ltd. was founded in 1992 and is based in Nanyang, China.",
